snippet.textDisplay: I was listening to this song x amount of times. I loved the sound when I listened to it the first time. I am not Indian. This song was on the radio when I went to work in India, it was on the radio when I went to dinner with friends in India and it was on the radio when I went to the beach with my Indian friends. They taught me the lyrics and I sang along after I finally learnt the lyrics! It is still one of my favorite songs made in India. Even after such a long time.
